lead_paragraph: Austria's World Cup giant slalom champion Eva-Maria Brem has broken her left leg in a training fall and will be out for the Alpine ski season, a team doctor said on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Alpine Skiing: Austria's Brem Breaks Leg, Out for Season
